The reunion begins with the "Tres Amigas," Vicki, Tamra and Shannon, rehashing their whirlwind trip to Mexico, which sparks some unexpected resentment from Gina. Vicki reflects on her year of unsuccessfully getting Steve to propose, as well as her past relationships. New housewife Gina opens up about her divorce. And sparks fly when Vicki and Kelly go head-to-head, culminating in a shocking claim by Vicki.
